        "text_CY9rBg": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h5><strong>Eco Foam Hot Tubs</strong></h5><p>Foam insulation is a game-changer for hot tubs, and our new foam spas are leading the charge. The foam core at the heart of our rigid models means the hot tub is up to 50% more thermally efficient, giving you cheaper bills whilst being better for the environment. The newest foam spas are made up of 3 models: the Garda, the Tahoe and the Como, each featuring a different shape and available in a range of 4 styles.</p><h5><strong>Inflatable Hot Tubs</strong></h5><p>Add a touch of luxury to your outdoor space, with our collection of inflatable hot tubs, the most indulgent way to relax all year round. Available in a variety of sizes, shapes and designs, accommodating up to 6 people, our Wave hot tubs are perfect for enjoying on your own or spending quality time with friends and family.<br/><br/><br/><br/></p>",
            "text_font": "body",
            "text_size": "subtext-md",
            "text_max_size": 32,
